properties.headline: Gale Warning issued February 7 at 6:56PM EST until February 7 at 11:00PM EST by NWS Boston/Norton MA
properties.description:
* WHAT...West winds 20 to 25 kt with gusts up to 35 kt and seas 2
to 4 feet, but up to 6 feet at the bay entrance.

* WHERE...Narragansett Bay.

* WHEN...Until 11 PM EST this evening.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds will cause hazardous seas which could
capsize or damage vessels and reduce visibility.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should alter plans to avoid these hazardous conditions.
Remain in port, seek safe harbor, alter course, and/or secure the
vessel for severe conditions.

NWSheadline: GALE WARNING IN EFFECT UNTIL 11 PM EST THIS EVENING... ...STORM WARNING IS CANCELLED
